text: The Saplings (, ) is a 1972 Russian Georgian comedy movie directed by Revaz Chkheidze and starring Jemal Gaganidze, Ramaz Chkhikvadze, Kakhi Kavsadze and Sesilia Takaishvili. ==Other websites== * Category:1972 comedy movies Category:Russian comedy movies Category:Georgian movies Category:Movies directed by Revaz Chkheidze Category:Movies set in Georgia (country)
title: The Saplings
